  "body": "## Description\r\n\r\nThis issue provides a place to track the increased CPU usage when switching to Altair.\r\n\r\nHere are some graphs when using https://github.com/paulhauner/lighthouse/commit/9db00d304b7fe2972e73427102ef90212d2def2b from https://github.com/paulhauner/lighthouse/tree/ad0-beta. You can see the increase after that Altair fork at ~19:12:\r\n\r\n![altair-block-times](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6660660/124900758-baa8c800-e024-11eb-84a4-97a27f8fc9ac.png)\r\n![altair-avg-load](https://user-images.githubusercontent.com/6660660/124900764-bb415e80-e024-11eb-8826-879900d13516.png)\r\n\r\nIt seems likely that #2415 will improve/fix these stats, especially the block processing ones.\r\n",
